-2620456x166_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>, <inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/7-2620456x167_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>, <inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/7-2620456x168_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>, <inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/7-2620456x169_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>, <inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/7-2620456x170_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>.</p><p>图1. 系统状态在脉冲控制律作用下的演化曲线</p><p>不确定项<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/7-2620456x172_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/7-2620456x173_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/7-2620456x174_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。不妨取<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/7-2620456x175_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/7-2620456x176_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/7-2620456x177_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/7-2620456x178_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/7-2620456x179_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/7-2620456x180_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/7-262045